Package: bmnr
Title: Bayesian Matrix Normal Regression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Josh",
           family = "Cowley",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "j.cowley1@ncl.ac.uk")
Maintainer: Josh Cowley <j.cowley1@ncl.ac.uk>
Description:
    Fits a Matrix normal distribution where the mean is a linear predictor,
    covariance across rows is assumed Gaussian process and covariance across
    columns is estimated.
